# WhataHotel proposals — agent rules

## Creating promos

All promos must use `createPromo()` from `src/lib/promoFactory.ts`. The agent provides only raw data — the factory and components handle all labels, formatting, and layout.

Agents edit only `src/data/promo-N.ts` and `src/data/promos.ts`. Never edit types, components, or the factory.

## Hardcoded UI (do not set or override)

These labels and sections are hardcoded in the components. The agent must not attempt to provide or change them:

- **"Room Highlights"** — title + door-open icon (RoomCard)
- **"Exclusive Perks"** — heading (PromoPage)
- **"Rate & pricing breakdown"** — heading (ProposalInvestment)
- **"Avg. Daily Rate (ADR)"** + **"Per night"** — labels (ProposalInvestment)
- **"Grand Total (incl. taxes & fees)"** — label (ProposalInvestment + ComparisonOverview)
- **"Rate Comparisons"** — table heading (ComparisonOverview)
- **"Book Now"** + **"Secure booking opens on WhataHotel.com in a new tab."** — button (RoomCard)
- **"Destination"** — label (CityHeroImage)
- **5 stars** — star row (HotelIdentity)
- **"by Lorraine Travel"** — masthead logo
- **App Download** — all text, URLs, icons
- **Contact Footer** — "Questions? Contact your advisor", "Lorraine Travel", email

## What the agent provides via createPromo()

- `PromoInput`: `id`, `title`, `dates`, `client?`, `cityImageUrl?`, `cityImageAlt?`
- `HotelInput[]`: `name`, `location`, `heroImageUrl`, `heroAlt`
- `RoomInput[]`: `name`, `subtitle`, `badgeText`, `adr`, `grandTotal`, `nights`, `checkIn`, `checkOut`, `bookUrl`, `images?`, `roomHighlights[]`, `perks[]`
